Detailed Description

cvmx_bbp_rx0_rfif_dma_wr_0_intr_status

HMM Interrupt Status Indicates the interrupt status after the interrupt enable/mask. When both the specific interrupt raw status and interrupt mask is set, an interrupt is asserted. This register represents the interrupt signal sento the controller.
